### Royal Parks Half Marathon - 11 April 2021
The stunning 13.1 mile route takes in the capital’s world-famous landmarks on
closed roads and four of London’s famous Royal Parks.
### London Landmarks Half Marathon - 23 May 2021
London Landmarks is one of the most exciting new events in London. From
cultural landmarks and heritage to the city's quirky and hidden secrets,
runners get to explore the capital on a route like no other.
### Edinburgh Marathon Festival - 29/30 May 2021
Scotland’s largest running festival of its kind. Fast and flat with courses
including the marathon, half marathon, 10K and 5K. It's ideal if it’s your
first race or if you are looking for a personal best.
### Bath Half Marathon - 5 September 2021
One of the longest-established and most popular city centre road events in the
UK. The Bath course is fast and flat, making it suitable for all abilities.
